OL,3,CDemocratic oversight measures for NI
OL,4,CBrexit rules are 'insufficient', peers
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThe framework requires checks and
OL,8,Fcustoms paperwork on goods moving from
OL,9,FGreat Britain into the region.
OL,11,FIt also includes a series of measures
OL,12,Fdesigned to address concerns that
OL,13,Fpoliticians and businesses in Northern
OL,14,FIreland have a limited role in
OL,15,Finfluencing the post-Brexit rules that
OL,16,Fapply in the region.
OL,18,FThis included the establishment of a
OL,19,Fdedicated committee at the Assembly to
OL,20,Fscrutinise EU law changes proposed to
OL,21,Fcome into effect in Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
