OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThe committee of peers assessed the
OL,8,Feffectiveness of the committee and the
OL,9,Fbrake, as well as a provision that
OL,10,Fallows stakeholders from Northern
OL,11,FIreland to attend certain joint UK-EU
OL,12,Fmeetings.
OL,14,FThe committee heard evidence from a
OL,15,Frange of witnesses, including the
OL,16,FFederation of Small Businesses
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland, the Ulster Farmers'
OL,18,FUnion and Northern Ireland Retail
OL,19,FConsortium.
