OL,7,FThe committee urged the Government to
OL,8,F"urgently consider" how to simplify
OL,9,Fthe framework arrangements, which it
OL,10,Fdescribed as a "complex and opaque
OL,11,Fstructure" that is difficult for
OL,12,Fbusiness and civil society
OL,13,Fstakeholders to navigate.
