OL,7,FIt found a need to address
OL,8,Fdifficulties faced by business due to
OL,9,Fthe absence of a centralised register
OL,10,Fof applicable EU laws in Northern
OL,11,FIreland, which requires them to spend
OL,12,Ftime and resources tracking
OL,13,Fdevelopments on laws applicable to
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FThe peers also found that the
OL,17,FGovernment's Trader Support Service
OL,18,Ffor businesses trying to navigate the
OL,19,Frules is "not providing a good quality
OL,20,Fof service".
