OL,7,FThe committee recommended a new unit
OL,8,Fin the Cabinet Office responsible for
OL,9,Fregulatory divergence and a "one stop
OL,10,Fshop" where businesses can access
OL,11,Frelevant information about EU laws
OL,12,Fthat apply in Northern Ireland.
