OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FPeers also expressed concern that the
OL,8,Fdemocratic scrutiny committee at
OL,9,FStormont does not have sufficient time
OL,10,For resources to effectively assess law
OL,11,Fchanges proposed to the region. That
OL,12,Fwas also a main finding in a recently
OL,13,Fpublished Government-commissioned
OL,14,Freview of the arrangements undertaken
OL,15,Fby Lord Murphy.
OL,17,FThe committee said the Stormont Brake
OL,18,Fwas a "highly political topic" and
OL,19,Fpeers noted the view expressed by some
OL,20,Fwitnesses that the mechanism was
OL,21,F"oversold".
