OL,7,FThey urged the Government to be "more
OL,8,Ftransparent" about the function of the
OL,9,Fbrake so that it can be used
OL,10,F"productively as a mechanism for
OL,11,Fpromoting dialogue" between it and the
OL,12,FAssembly.
OL,14,FCommenting on the report, Lord
OL,15,FCarlile, chairman of the committee,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Our report comes at a pivotal
OL,17,Fmoment for Northern Ireland and the
OL,18,FUK. As the Government pursues a reset
OL,19,Fin UK-EU relations, it is vital that
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland's voice is
OL,21,Frepresented and heard.
