OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"The potential agreements on sanitary
OL,8,Fand phytosanitary and energy
OL,9,Farrangements could have significant
OL,10,Fimplications for Northern Ireland's
OL,11,Fplace in the UK internal market, and
OL,12,Ffor how the UK consults the EU on the
OL,13,Fapplication of EU law.
OL,15,F"We strongly support proposals to
OL,16,Fenhance Northern Ireland's voice early
OL,17,Fin the EU legislative process,
OL,18,Fincluding through better resourcing of
OL,19,Fthe UK Mission in Brussels and closer
OL,20,Fcollaboration with the Northern
OL,21,FIreland Civil Service.
