OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"It was clear from the concerns raised
OL,8,Fby businesses, civil society and
OL,9,Fpolitical representatives ` both in
OL,10,Fformal evidence and during our visit
OL,11,Fto Newry and Belfast ` that the
OL,12,Fdemocratic deficit in Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fremains unresolved.
OL,15,F"Despite differing views among
OL,16,Fmembers, we agree that meaningful
OL,17,Fengagement, transparency, and public
OL,18,Funderstanding must be urgently
OL,19,Fimproved for the benefit of all
OL,20,Fcommunities in Northern Ireland."
